              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>This dancer may be found in one of the many scattered mercenary groups that hail from the desert. She will unleash the Spirit of Omen: Dendro Spirit-Serpent contained within her weapon to fight alongside her after taking a certain amount of damage. This will cause her to <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">enter an Infused Form</span>. If <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">the Spirit-Serpent is defeated</span>, she will enter a weakened state for a fixed amount of time thereafter.</p>"
